，見fb嗰走火通道圖有6x檔<br />\n但都多人排<br />\n<br />\nBtw好心租鋪咪撚見多人排<br />\n就將入場費加到廿蚊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"我反而唔太介意排隊，同時俾入場費，最怕入到去檔口少，冇嘢啱買/或者買唔落手。 <br />\n已罰過黃埔場，可能因為場地太細，所以太少檔口，未能夠盡情大大力罰。<br />\n希望銅鑼灣/觀塘/紅磡恒藝/長沙灣及其他場爭氣吖"},{"pid":"fb6eb918a1bad02d9eb35dcd96ec90031fa91f40","tid":1832480,"uid":82856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:41:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e041a74669209b490fe0008f08b1d86a60ee457c","tid":1832480,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:56:30.000Z","msg":"依個要推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定去！！！！"},{"pid":"e7bc1f82ea5895b2bdd16bbb608ceeda79f9fac1","tid":1832480,"uid":42548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T01:06:48.000Z","msg":"時代夾面，沾面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7545e75adcf480326528babb79c48ca544efab0","tid":1832480,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5055352270eaa17da57aff1956526fe54fea2647","tid":1832480,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c238c1b79fbd8553b01c80f169b9e8d910c4f8","tid":1832480,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n多謝樓主咁有心"}]}